112624.title: 25 oz. New Belgium Fat Tire Amber Ale

115555.description: Absolut Elyx is the result of manual processes, authentic craftsmanship, and human supervision through every detail of production. Crafted from single estate wheat and distilled by hand in a 1921 copper still to create a remarkably silky vodka.
115555.title: Absolut Elyx

115636.description: Discover a unique vodka experience when French craftsmanship, superior ingredients, and a distinct distilling process merge to create a smooth taste that brings people together for moments of excellence.
115636.title: Grey Goose

115637.description: After a sip of Ketel One Vodka, you'll taste a crisp, unmistakable coolness.
115637.title: Ketel One

115639.description: The Reyka distillery--Iceland’s first distillery--is found in Borgarnes, Iceland. Located 74km outside of Reykjavik, this coastal village is removed from industrial life and surrounded by wonderful natural resources. Clean and markedly smooth, Reyka is produced with glacial water for a simple, crisp taste.
115639.title: Reyka

115640.description: Stoli Ohranj has a light and floral aroma of orange zest and essential oils, the more top scents of orange blossom balanced by richer elements of orange liqueur and marmalade. Stoli Ohranj has orange cream on its palate, hints of dark chocolate and more varied flavors of tangerine, mandarin and kumquat, and a lingering fresh zesty note of lemon.
115640.title: Stolichnaya Ohranj

115642.description: Stolichnaya Premium Vodka is a classically-styled, exceptionally smooth vodka. Crystal clear in color with marshmallow, mineral, and mild fruit peel aromas. A soft, supple entry leads to a smooth, medium bodied palate with pastry frosting, talc, and citrus rind flavors. Finishes with a clean, lightly sweet, sugar dust, wet straw, and balanced pepper fade.
115642.title: Stolichnaya

115643.description: Tito’s Handmade Vodka is a corn-based vodka produced in Austin at Texas’ oldest legal distillery. They make it in batches, use old-fashioned pot stills, and taste-test every batch. Tito’s Handmade Vodka is designed to be savored by spirit connoisseurs and everyday drinkers alike. Their process, similar to those used to make fine single malt scotches and high-end French cognacs, requires more skill and effort than others, but it's well worth it. Naturally gluten-free.
115643.title: Tito's Handmade Vodka

115655.description: Belvedere, the world's first luxury vodka, is authentic and natural, handcrafted the way Polish vodka has been made for over 600 years.
115655.title: Belvedere

115656.description: Prairie's single vintage organic corn is distilled to taste, not a prescribed number of times. That's because climate, soil, and moisture levels give each small batch its own unique character. Preserving that character takes personal attention, giving our vodka an award-winning taste that can stand on its own. With hints of melon and pear on the nose, creaminess on the palate, and a bright, smooth finish, Prairie is among the world's most luxurious vodkas.
115656.title: Prairie Vodka

115769.description: Smirnoff is the world's No. 1 vodka. Its classic taste has inspired other varieties throughout all four corners of the globe.
115769.title: Smirnoff

115770.description: Absolut is made exclusively from natural ingredients, and unlike other vodkas, it doesn't contain any added sugar. In fact, Absolut is as pure as vodka can be. Rich, full-bodied and complex, yet smooth and mellow with a distinct character of grain, followed by a hint of dried fruit.
115770.title: Absolut

115771.description: Elevating centuries of vodka tradition to hi-tech art, Elit by Stolichnaya is the inception of ultra-luxury vodka. A spirit of breathtaking clarity and flawless molecular composition, it is born from an obsession with accuracy and stands on five pillars of perfection: source, filtration, purification, bottling, and packaging. This is vodka at its most precise.
115771.title: Stolichnaya Elit

115772.description: Stoli Vanil offers elegant aromas of vanilla pod, crème anglaise, and chocolate, with undertones of toasted buttery grain, but without the heavy cloying sweetness of some vanilla vodkas. Stoli Vanil’s palate brings a creamy sweetness to the fore, but it is light and balanced, with cocoa powder, white pepper, and sweet spicy notes.
115772.title: Stolichnaya Vanil
